  <body>
   <p>John Halperin, well-known "Labor Friend", does not want to abide with the demands of the Workers to recognize the Amalgamated and a 44-hour week. Therefore, the Workers opened a strike.</p>
   <p>John Halperin's Shop is located at Franklin and Van Buren Streets.</p>
